name:               mauke
version:            0.1.0.0
synopsis:           MauKe: Maude inspired K
description:        Please see README.md
homepage:           http://github.com/ehildenb/mauke
license:            BSD3
license-file:       LICENSE
author:             Everett Hildenbrandt
maintainer:         hildenb2@illinois.edu
